{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8b3fca8f6d","title":"视察人民大会堂时的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4bfaf8b6cf","index":0,"year":1959,"month":9,"day":5,"articleId":"8b3fca8f6d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"0ad0e69946","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8b3fca8f6d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"1959年9月5日，毛泽东视察人民大会堂工程。本篇一是毛泽东视察了礼堂的一二层和上海厅后的指示；本篇二是毛泽东看了宴会厅，询问了工程情况后的指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"69b7962e2b","type":"title","text":"视察人民大会堂时的指示”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8b3fca8f6d"},{"id":"0ad0e69946","type":"paragraph","text":"人民大会堂的建成确实是成绩伟大，你们这么大的功劳，是不是立块碑吧！那将多大呀！照相吧！也站不下呀！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8b3fca8f6d"},{"id":"168882731f","type":"paragraph","text":"要向老红军学习，不为名，不为利，不计报酬，不怕轴性。红军打仗也没有礼拜大，没有休息，没有加班费，还是学习老红军吧，要和老红军一样。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8b3fca8f6d"},{"id":"bde8e11ac6","type":"paragraph","text":"大跃进就是好，有人说天跃进不好，十三陵水库，人民大会堂就是大跃进的产物。没有大跃进就没有大会堂。让那些右派来看看，究竟是不是大跃进！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8b3fca8f6d"}],"page":{"id":"8c5aa402e8","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8b3fca8f6d","start":345,"end":345}}}},"__N_SSG":true}